Package algonquin.cst2335.cst2335_finalproject

Class CcyListItem

java.lang.Object
algonquin.cst2335.cst2335_finalproject.CcyListItem
public class CcyListItem extends Object
This class is used to store details about a currency conversion, including the original currency unit, original amount, converted currency unit, converted amount, and the time when the conversion was made.
